# Citation File Format — https://citation-file-format.github.io/
# GitHub reads this to render a "Cite this repository" button.
# Keep this file in sync with docs/citation.rst.
cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite the paper below (preferred) and the software."
title: "COSMO: COarse-grained Simulation of intrinsically disordered prOteins with OpenMM"
abstract: >-
  COSMO is a coarse-grained simulation engine for intrinsically disordered
  proteins and related biomolecules, built on OpenMM. It implements the HPS
  hydropathy-scale force fields (hps_urry / hps_kr / hps_ss) and the Mpipi model,
  and includes a per-codon co-translational-synthesis protocol (CSP) ported from
  the topo project.
type: software
authors:
